==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Up-train
<hw>Up"-train`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>. <sn>1.</sn> <def>A train going in the
direction of the metropolis or the main terminus.</def>
<mark>[Eng.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>A train going in the direction conventionally called
<xex>up</xex>.</def> <mark>[U. S.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Upturn</ent>⟦br⟧
